## Known Projection Limitations

List ambiguities or missing Core information that may limit ReimagineEpic.

| Limitation | Why It Matters | Recommended Handling |
|---|---|---|

Examples:

- preserved strategic need is not explicit
- desired capability boundary is ambiguous
- replacement principles are underspecified
- abstraction replacement rules are unclear
- constraints are not prioritized
- escalation boundaries are ambiguous
